embeds.title: 77er Bot Musikmen√º
embeds.description:
`/music` - Displays all available music commands.
`/play` - Plays music.
`/playprevius` - Plays the previous music.
`/queue` - Displays the queue of music.
`/skip` - Skip to the next song.
`/pause` - Pauses the music.
`/resume` - Resume music playback.
`/loopmusic` - Continues the music in a loop.
`/unloopmusic` - Stops the music from looping.
`/shuffle` - Shuffles the music in the queue.
`/stopmusic` - Stop the music.
embeds.author: Ben // Zerofour // 77er Bot // GG
